{"h842716e2geca9g41c2gb3c0g78ae592eae2d": ["*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_Dead.html", "60ff9f1c-7822-e66e-9e79-304609b245b0"], "h9f37736ag949bg44b8g9306g8bc53b6da324": ["*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_Dead.html", "447c156d-8d50-3391-da34-38a4977ebb32"], "h882f0c18g8b18g4893g95c1gcc603cd4e679": ["*The corpse regards you lifelessly.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_Dead.html", "d0d905a2-27d8-606e-67a9-c22933146d9d"], "hc2d3ca61g4039g4c7bgb1fcgb004c9f75d99": ["Who are you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_Dead.html", "10083b90-6849-2de4-0183-de052dd82baa"], "he53f27bfga4dag4e2bgb990g7f71255e8707": ["Brynna... a faithful... servant to... the Absolute...", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_Dead.html", "c45e72e5-3117-d3b7-c85c-e76b3136a967"], "ha5664458g4988g4011g9a7eg4081d13dc9f4": ["What were you doing in the forest?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_Dead.html", "2a9f2625-feda-e3b3-410a-3ba48a0f6117"], "hcd01283eg2cb7g4c04gabbcgc4c372b5c299": ["Serving... the Absolute... following... her True Souls...", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_Dead.html", "347e682e-75cf-cf4f-181d-303277afca35"], "h03d4aec3g303cg4698ga868g8ee8e7516c07": ["How did you die?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_Dead.html", "4b8521cc-c456-6eda-a414-e2622086919e"], "h9a9138cbg1682g43c1g93cag57af35c6dc27": ["Tell me about the Absolute.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_Dead.html", "89698a55-f07d-d370-86a0-32898873d912"], "h01b9c347gddf1g4cf0gb294g0a049139d0a1": ["Our leader... our goddess... our future... bow to her... or die...", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_Dead.html", "c85cdff8-3603-9ad7-a3f1-0201fa50c66b"], "h344719eeg2e07g457bg8c77g56e34d024a35": ["What is a 'True Soul'?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_Dead.html", "14eaf806-a296-6289-9f8c-7fb1cf55a163"], "h4f583c9egbe5eg4b26g9029gb1db054f9a46": ["The Absolute's... chosen few... my brother... they hear... her words...", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_Dead.html", "9cec2a98-1112-0b68-0c16-e1cfce23ca5a"], "hcf3d562cgd4c3g4098ga7cag42ad6027e21c": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_Dead.html", "be3263b9-9ba9-2b7e-686a-091060c5e326"], "h1e0a9516gf737g4b06ga986g08315a15e211": ["*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_Dead.html", "f4faa226-cc24-4bc6-3b6e-e00463d75d31"]}